            <div class="page-contents__inner">
              <p class="page-contents__title">Page contents</p>
              <div class="page-contents__list-wrapper">
                <div class="grid-wrap">
                  <div class="grid-col desktop-grid-one-half">
                    <ul class="linklist page-contents__list">
                      <li><a href="#section-1">Section 1 testing</a></li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div class="grid-col desktop-grid-one-half">
                    <ul class="linklist page-contents__list">
                      <li><a href="#section-2">Section 2 testing</a></li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid-wrap">
            <div class="grid-col desktop-grid-two-thirds desktop-grid-pad-right">
              <div class="panel panel--inform" id="section-1">
                <p class="panel__title">Something about a checklist</p>
                <div class="panel__copy">
                  <ul>
                    <li>You can’t order bins or boxes if you don’t have somewhere to store them off the street.</li>
                    <li>If they contained an item we do not collect</li>
                    <li>If they were not out by 7am</li>
                    <li>If they were not visible from the road</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>

