              <div class="panel media">
                <img class="img" alt="Green wheelie bin" src="/ui/images/waste/green-wheelie-bin.png">
                <div class="media__content">
                  <p class="panel__title--minor">Looking for the Green Wheelie Bin?</p>
                  <div class="panel__copy--small">
                    <p>Sign up and pay for our <a href="#">garden waste collection</a>.</p>
                    <p>If your green wheelie bin is damaged you have to order and pay for new one, unless we damaged it.</p>
